Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}7000万で許しちゃおう</c.japanese>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}さすがリーダー 器がでかい</c.japanese>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（シンシア）アビー</c.japanese>
